name: Basic Edit
description: Basic edits consist of facial touch ups, lighting fixes, and color fixes. These edits are minor for an absolute gorgeous photo. The outcome will look all natural and beautiful. Basic edits cost 2 dollars PER picture. Send us a myspace message with your picture, email, and what you want done to your picture once you have purchased it.

name: Advanced Edit
description: Advanced Edits consist of facial touch ups, lighting fixes, color fixes (picture itself, and hair, eyes, or makeup), and resizing/deletion of body and/or face. These edits will make your image look absolutely flawless. If you want an advanced, please give details on what you want done. Advanced edits cost 4 dollars PER picture. Send us a myspace message with your picture, email, and what you want done to your picture once you have purchased it.

name: Special Edits
description: Special Edits are special things you want done to your picture that are not in Basic/Advanced edits. Each picture will cost 5 dollars. Send us a myspace message with your picture, email, and what you want done to your picture. Send us a myspace message with your picture, email, and what you want done to your picture once you have purchased it.

name: Graphics
description:
Graphics can be anything from Train/Group Graphics, to support codes, banners, and much more. Each graphic costs 10 dollars, (Trains/Groups cost 20, must purchase twice or you'll only receive a header for your group/train).
Send us a myspace message with your picture, email, and what you want done to your picture.
